answers.answer: And it doesnt mean anything is wrong with you, your babies like it in there its all cozy :)

Nothing's wrong, your baby is just nice and cozy inside mommy. My son was the same way, heck at 40 weeks he had barely even dropped, he thought he had it made in there, used my ribs as a foot rest everyday all day!! Lol

Some woman just don't dialate etc. My cousin has had five children and has had to be scheduled for c section everytime because even if they try to induce her her body refuses to dialate. You're doing something amazing regardless of how it finally has to happen don't get down babe.

Im 39 weeks.  Im being induced because i have gestational diabetes and my baby girl is large.    I was hoping to have at least to have one natural pregnancy.  because i am having my tubes tied after i have her tommorow

Don't feel bad!  I have been induced with all 3 of mine.  Its not important how they get here, it getting them here so u get to meet em!  Lol you can still be induced and have a natural labor.  I did with #2 and 3.  I was able to move around freely, rock in the rocking chair, and no epidural!  Nothings wrong with u at all.  Good luck to u.

title: un wanted induction
